<p>The <a href="#menu_group_command-class">MENU_GROUP_COMMAND</a> class manages the command menus for coalitions, which allow players to execute functions during mission execution.
You can add menus with the <a href="#menu_group_command-new-menugroup-the-the-a-an">MENU_GROUP_COMMAND:New()</a> method, which constructs a MENU_GROUP_COMMAND object and returns you the object reference.
Using this object reference, you can then remove ALL the menus and submenus underlying automatically with <a href="#menu_group_command-remove-self">MENU_GROUP_COMMAND:Remove()</a>.</p>
